{"tid":2189213,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"【蘋果踢爆】何君堯祖墳霸官地 擬率村民抗議求「放生」 民政處逾1年未執法","createTime":"2020-09-04T17:18:54.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-04T17:58:37.000Z","uid":240362,"like":5,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"86cf15e16ff89b2232c06b87fae38b9e6f39e525","tid":2189213,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-04T17:18:54.000Z","msg":"新界西立法會議員何君堯在去年7.21元朗恐襲當日與在場白衣人握手言歡，更向對方表示「辛苦晒」；何雙親的墳墓事後被塗污破壞，同時被揭發非法霸佔官地，事件至今相隔逾1年，當局依然不作取締，墓地違規情況依舊。《蘋果》取得良田村村委會近日的通告，顯示何君堯曾要求民政事務局局長徐英偉將墓園按現狀重新劃界，更鼓動村民到民政署及地政署抗議施壓。<br />\n<br />\n通告指，何君堯已向民政局局長徐英偉反映良田村墓園事宜，要求「重新按現狀劃界」；又指現時墓園先導計劃出現多重問題，呼籲村民團結「領隊去民政署／地政署抗議」，稱墓園規劃是整個新界鄉要關注的事情，疫情緩和後有必要與鄉委會討論。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200905/4XNXGG65BNDBZFEUVIPQNPT534/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200905%2F4XNXGG65BNDBZFEUVIPQNPT534%2F&d=RlZLtXxvTyjhSejQ4AJs45R%2B4kUINcy65scadR%2F1ewI%3D&h=53f7e318\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200905%2F4XNXGG65BNDBZFEUVIPQNPT534%2F&h=7e4a5cac\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200905/4XNXGG65BNDBZFEUVIPQNPT534/</a>"},{"pid":"3db0ee783c49c94159dda5e18b1c94fdfe4c7448","tid":2189213,"uid":201359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-04T17:21:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fb25766aa2a040e5561c2d50db0d3f1bcf4becf3","tid":2189213,"uid":232157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-04T17:25:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8d844